<h2 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; line-height: 46px; margin-top: 20px; color: rgb(47, 45, 45); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;">Purpose of Terms and Conditions</h2><p style="margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45);">The <u>purpose</u> of terms and </span><font color="#000000" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">conditions</font><font color="#2f2d2d"> is to provide a set of instructions for all parties of a contract. They also offer guidance to courts regarding the intent and purpose of the transaction at the time it was created.</font></p><p style="margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(47, 45, 45); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;">Elements of terms and <span style="font-family: Impact;">conditions</span> may include:</p><ul style="margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 40px; overflow: hidden; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;"><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(231, 156, 156);">Rights</span></li><li style="padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;"><font color="#00ff00">Obligations</font></li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Duties</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Roles</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Responsibilities</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Consideration</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Contact info</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Signature lines</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Handling disputes</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Important dates</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Deliverables</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Payment terms</li><li style="color: rgb(47, 45, 45); padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">Limitations</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(47, 45, 45); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;">Terms and conditions exist to inform people of their rights when engaging in a business transaction. They carry legal implications of which both parties should be aware. Carefully review all contracts before signing them since many do not let you cancel them without penalty before fulfilling your obligations.</p>